{"tid":1912534,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧哈拉：摩連奴再冇藉口","createTime":"2020-03-06T06:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T11:11:52.000Z","uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5388d26294ea7e78ae8db5fb2e5b43dc557d44d","tid":1912534,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴睇中約拿芬大衛頂奧巴美揚<br />\n<br />\n熱刺在足總盃16強主場不敵諾域治，各賽事合計連輸4場。奧哈拉表示：「我厭倦藉口了，之前我撐過摩佬，他缺少了卡尼及孫興民，他嘗試取勝但不成功。然而，那種因傷兵等問題而為熱刺感到可惜的負面感覺，不要了！你要取得成績，球隊也夠強去應付諾域治。摩佬再沒藉口。」<br />\n<br />\n問到前主帥普捷天奴有沒有機會回歸，奧哈拉說：「會，為何不會？普捷天奴有機會歸位，他仍未有工作，熱刺球迷仍然喜歡他，因此有可能呀。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=1f21fbfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"8e2ad2077ca048963203a750e3c084e907fe282d","tid":1912534,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"ohara 由熱刺半主力<br />\n踢到英甲都唔要"},{"pid":"276bdf5509f49f51b0bc68f6d03b557541ce06cb","tid":1912534,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"摩廢奴教到，好似李城咁都拎到冠軍我就服喇。<br />\n根本廢奴套野就out晒"},{"pid":"9de6c3cb591d15d5a94b9d195be8ed5fe2e6d3fa","tid":1912534,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061a869af9fe6e2e7d9c0fd0a2c3d72b089a4058","tid":1912534,"uid":49891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e2ad2077ca048963203a750e3c084e907fe282d","tid":1912534,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"ohara 由熱刺半主力<br />\n踢到英甲都唔要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:44:41.000Z","msg":"當年佢嚟香港同南華踢<br />\n唔知鏟到邊個比人噓足成場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dec5c433749583e0bde653c3ee02062d125aa1f","tid":1912534,"uid":66839,"like":1,"dislike":0